Thanks for investigation this, Frank. The framework does not support properly contribution of multiple pages that extend AbstractTaskEditorPage even though there are no checks to explicitly prevent this. Allowing it would create a number of problems due to having multiple edit models of the same task data. This problem needs to be addressed within TBR by changing the implementation of the editor pages to extend TaskFormPage instead.

Since TBR isn't shipped I won't assign this for 1.0 but we should consider fixing this. Frank, I would suggest removing the bundles from your workspace or runtime configuration if the problem gets in the way of using the task editor.
Kilian, I think the patch at https://git.eclipse.org/r/#/c/8360/ is ready to be merged.
